659
00:33:39.234 --> 00:33:43.847
A donation to the NYPD Museum?

660
00:33:45.110 --> 00:33:47.634
Brian's doing better.

661
00:33:47.677 --> 00:33:50.332
He is. thank you.

662
00:33:50.376 --> 00:33:52.682
Thought you weren't coming in
for a few weeks.

663
