I told Jimmy
I'd relieve him for a few hours.

664
00:33:55.250 --> 00:33:56.643
I could use the break.

665
00:33:56.686 --> 00:33:59.950
Things are bad
if work's a break.

666
00:33:59.994 --> 00:34:02.344
Actually. things are very good.

667
00:34:02.388 --> 00:34:04.346
Brian is breathing on his own.

668
00:34:04.390 --> 00:34:06.522
he's complaining
about hospital food.

669
00:34:06.566 --> 00:34:09.525
and they're gonna release him
tomorrow.

670
00:34:10.570 --> 00:34:12.528
Good news.

671
00:34:12.572 --> 00:34:14.269
Well. maybe you should

672
00:34:14.313 --> 00:34:16.532
