to the officer's family.

679
00:34:48.434 --> 00:34:50.436
And now I know.

680
00:34:51.828 --> 00:34:53.917
Thank you.

681
00:35:06.191 --> 00:35:09.281
Son of a bitch. he set us up.
I told you not to trust him.

682
00:35:09.324 --> 00:35:10.369
We don't know that yet.

683
00:35:10.412 --> 00:35:11.979
Of course he set us up.

684
00:35:12.022 --> 00:35:14.392
He got the hell out of there
right before the boxes exploded.

685
00:35:14.416 --> 00:35:16.723
How the hell would he know?!
He knew what was coming.

686
00:35:16.766 --> 00:35:19.682
Then why did he go back
to his apartment? What?

687
00:35:20.770 --> 00:35:22.163
Look at the ankle monitor.

688
00:35:22.207 --> 00:35:23.686
It proves that he's there.

689
00:35:23.730 --> 00:35:25.253
Then. what happened?

690
00:35:25.297 --> 00:35:27.449
Well. I'll let you
know after I see him. No. no. no. no.

691
00:35:27.473 --> 00:35:29.214
You'll let 'em know
after wesee him.

692
00:35:29.257 --> 00:35:30.432
We're going with you.

693
00:35:35.872 --> 00:35:37.352
Let's go.

694
00:35:46.100 --> 00:35:48.450
