783
00:40:22.681 --> 00:40:24.683
No.

784
00:40:24.726 --> 00:40:27.163
Because it is
the kind of activity

785
00:40:27.207 --> 00:40:29.818
where even
if you do everything perfectly.

786
00:40:29.862 --> 00:40:32.604
there's no guarantee of a fish.

787
00:40:32.647 --> 00:40:36.651
And what else is like that.
if I'm hearing you correctly?

788
00:40:36.695 --> 00:40:39.698
Being a boss.

789
00:40:39.741 --> 00:40:44.050
One slipup. and the searchlight
comes on hot and fast.

790
00:40:44.093 --> 00:40:46.356
Tell me about it.

791
00:40:48.402 --> 00:40:51.536
Pop told me I took
the press conference personally.

792
00:40:51.579 --> 00:40:54.016
That I was expecting
you'd act more like

793
00:40:54.060 --> 00:40:55.931
a protective father than the PC.

794
00:40:55.975 --> 00:40:57.977
And what do you think?

795
00:40:58.020 --> 00:41:01.502
That my mistake was acting
like a respectful daughter.

796
00:41:01.546 --> 00:41:04.026
letting you have the last word.

797
00:41:07.160 --> 00:41:09.118
And the next time?

798
00:41:09.162 --> 00:41:12.426
I will always
be respectful of you.

799
00:41:12.470 --> 00:41:15.429
Couldn't be
any other way. but...

800
00:41:15.473 --> 00:41:18.084
I need to respect
my office. too.

801
00:41:22.567 --> 00:41:26.614
And maybe keep the joint press
conferences to a minimum.

802
00:41:26.658 --> 00:41:29.791
Yeah. That. too.

803
00:41:31.184 --> 00:41:33.447
Ooh.

804
00:41:33.491 --> 00:41:35.928
Well. what do you know.

805
00:41:35.971 --> 00:41:37.973
Results.

